<!-- ============ 母题 ============ -->

<section>
  <h2><span class="num">iv.</span>三道母题</h2>
  <p>覆盖大纲 A 级目标的最小子集。先合上答案做，做完再展开核对。</p>

  <!-- 母题 1 -->

  <div class="problem">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="problem-num">i.</span>
      <span class="problem-title">Cobb-Douglas 成本最小化</span>
      <span class="problem-source">PPT § 78</span>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-stmt">
      已知生产函数 $Q = L^{2/3}\, K^{1/3}$，劳动价格 $w=2$，资本价格 $r=1$。求 $Q=800$ 时实现成本最小化的 $L^*,\ K^*,\ C^*$。
    </div>
    <details class="solution">
      <summary>展开解答</summary>
      <div class="solution-body">
        <span class="step"><strong>步 1.</strong> 算 MRTS：$MP_L = \tfrac{2}{3}L^{-1/3}K^{1/3}$，$MP_K = \tfrac{1}{3}L^{2/3}K^{-2/3}$，相除得 $\mathrm{MRTS} = 2K/L$。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>步 2.</strong> 切线条件：$2K/L = w/r = 2 \Rightarrow K = L$。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>步 3.</strong> 代回生产函数：$L^{2/3}\cdot L^{1/3} = L = 800$。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>结果：</strong> $L^* = K^* = 800,\quad C^* = 2(800)+1(800) = 2400$。</span>
        <div class="tip">秒解技巧：Cobb-Douglas 在 $\mathrm{MRTS}=w/r$ 下永远得到 $K/L = (\beta/\alpha)(w/r)$，背下来。</div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>

  <!-- 母题 2 -->

  <div class="problem">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="problem-num">ii.</span>
      <span class="problem-title">从 MC 反推 TC 族</span>
      <span class="problem-source">PPT § 79</span>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-stmt">
      已知 $MC(Q) = 3Q^2 - 30Q + 100$，$TC(10) = 1000$。求 $FC$、$TC(Q)$、$VC(Q)$、$AC(Q)$、$AVC(Q)$。
    </div>
    <details class="solution">
      <summary>展开解答</summary>
      <div class="solution-body">
        <span class="step"><strong>步 1.</strong> 积分得 VC：$VC(Q) = \int MC\, dQ = Q^3 - 15Q^2 + 100Q$（用 $VC(0)=0$ 锚定常数）。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>步 2.</strong> 算 $VC(10) = 1000 - 1500 + 1000 = 500$。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>步 3.</strong> $FC = TC(10) - VC(10) = 1000 - 500 = 500$。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>结果：</strong></span>
        <span class="step">$\quad TC(Q) = Q^3 - 15Q^2 + 100Q + 500$</span>
        <span class="step">$\quad AC(Q) = Q^2 - 15Q + 100 + 500/Q$</span>
        <span class="step">$\quad AVC(Q) = Q^2 - 15Q + 100$</span>
        <div class="tip">关键技巧：永远用 $VC(0)=0$ 定积分常数。这类题没有别的入口。</div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>

  <!-- 母题 3 -->

  <div class="problem">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="problem-num">iii.</span>
      <span class="problem-title">短期-长期成本曲线关系（画图题）</span>
      <span class="problem-source">PPT § 56–61</span>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-stmt">
      画一组 $SAC_1, SAC_2, SAC_3$ 与 $LAC$，并回答：<br>
      ① 为什么 $LAC$ 是 $SAC$ 族的下包络线？<br>
      ② 哪个产量上 $SAC$ 与 $LAC$ 相切？切点是不是 $SAC$ 的最低点？<br>
      ③ 为什么 $LMC$ <strong>不是</strong> $SMC$ 的包络线？
    </div>
    <details class="solution">
      <summary>展开解答提示</summary>
      <div class="solution-body">
        <span class="step"><strong>① </strong>长期可调规模，所以每个产量上选最优工厂规模 → 最低成本 → 包络下方所有 SAC。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>② </strong>切点 = 该规模下生产该产量的最优。<strong>除非</strong>恰好是 LAC 最低点（CRS 临界），否则切点不是 SAC 的最低点。规模经济区切点在 SAC 最低点左侧；规模不经济区切点在右侧。</span>
        <span class="step"><strong>③ </strong>$LMC$ 是"按最优规模生产"时的 $SMC$ 值轨迹，只取每个 SMC 曲线的<strong>一个点</strong>，不是整段。所以 $LMC$ 不可能是 $SMC$ 的包络线。</span>
        <div class="tip">这题理解透了能秒杀本章 70% 的概念题。要详细画图就告诉我。</div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

